cterest mock fixture — plain text
=================================

This is the on-disk sample streamed by GET /api/media/:id/raw for the .txt media.
Editing it in the app and saving issues PUT /api/media/:id/raw, which overwrites
this very file. Plain text has no syntax highlighting — Monaco renders it as-is.

- no tokens here
- just lines
- line numbers live in the non-selectable left gutter
